     <h2 id="interior-split-page-header-full">
      ADMINISTRATIVE POLICIES &amp; COMPLIANCE
     </h2>
     <div id="section">
      <img alt="Upper corner of UCLA Murphy Hall Building" id="interior-split-hero-image" src="/img/APC_Image960w5.jpg"/>
     </div>
     <div id="interior-split-container">
      <div class="section clear-fix">
       <div class="section-text">
        <div class="section-header">
         ADMINISTRATIVE POLICIES &amp; COMPLIANCE OFFICE
        </div>
        <div class="section">
         <p>
          The Administrative Policies &amp; Compliance Office (APC) coordinates campus
                    compliance activities governed by the University's Whistleblower Policy and
                    Whistleblower Protection Policy.
         </p>
         <p>
          APC also assists and facilitates the promulgation of campus-wide
                    policies and procedures, and the issuance of delegations of authority.
         </p>
         <p>
          APC reports to the Vice Chancellor of Legal Affairs.
         </p>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
